question: Those in HS/College, was it/is it required to do community service?
comment:

I don't think it should be required for the whole school, but I don't see an issue for NHS or organizations like that to require it. And I do think teachers should be allowed to offer some extra credit to kids who volunteer. Community service is a great way to see part of the world and your community that needs help and is in poor condition, but in a safe and controlled manner. It won't do this for all kids but some kids may even be shocked by what they see and want to do more, to help, or develop future plans to better the community.
